title: Julian Jordan & TV Noise - Childish Grandpa (Original Mix).m
description:
RELEASE DATE	2013-07-01
LABELS	Spinnin Records
CATALOG #	SP679


A masterful production by teenage production wonder Julian Jordan, who teams up with home country peers TV Noise to bring you 'Childish Grandpa'. A wonderfully melodic and original release, which ticks the boxes of both progressive and electro genres. Turn the volume way up, cause everyone will dance to this! No doubt this will be a chart shredder!
